{"title":"给大山","authors":["李玲修"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":5,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给大山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李玲修"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，大山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生命的山！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你那么伟岸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"思维的云朵令人景仰；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你那么平易，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"知心的话儿同小鸟交谈；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你那么浑厚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肌肤下埋藏着闪光的矿岩；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你沉默寡言，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从不炫耀自己的富有与奉献！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你为小草捧出生命的沃土，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你为大树提供舒展的空间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你为放牧的孩子遮挡赤日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你为攀登的人们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪出弯弯曲曲的路线。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八面来风吹不弯你的身躯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雾障弥漫迷不了你的双眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滔滔洪水改不了你的本色，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泥石滚滚伤不了你的尊严！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风来了，你听取她的信息，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燕去了，你留下她的忠言，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"落雪了，你接纳她的滋润，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"播种了，你孕育着一个个春天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}